eventText: Deepak made the changes in the DD and sent it back to Dominik for approval.
Sambhaji sent the app store, Amazon, GA requirements to Dominik.
ACR sent a lots of feedback on the design draft.
Mariona asks Deepak, if Deepak will take care of the changes. Shantanu replied that he has already transferred the changes to Deepak.
Deepak says, he will implement the changes and will send the PDF. Mariona is fine with it.
Dominik says, we will use our own AWS S3 bucket.
Deepak completes the changes and resend the DD for approvals.
Dominik informs that the DD is with client now for approvals.
Shantanu sends the ACR app TOC, data for approvals to Dominik.
Dominik asks Shantanu to update the ACR timeline in Redmine.
